latestIgtvVideos.title: I needed to lose you to love me💔
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Sometimes there are people, places, objects and even thoughts that you need you let go off to become the best version of yourself. 🥲
.
You don’t need to hate those people/thoughts etc. but for your peace you need to maybe reduce the contact and conflict. They might come back as better incentives for doing great in life and the bonding might become even stronger, or you’ll find out it was best that you let them go.
.
